Description:
Easter Week sale! Take 10% off everything in the shop. Hurry - sale ends Saturday!
 These are beautiful 1980s-1990s style frames from Lady Stetson and Zyloware. The plastic frames are a bright mint green and are somewhat transparent.
Please note - these frames are very lightweight and somewhat flexible with a delicate design. They are not rigid like some other styles. Because they have been sitting in storage for over two decades, they may require some adjustment to regain all aspects of their original perfect shape.
They are deadstock "new old stock" frames - brand new and unworn.
Each pair comes with demo lenses with the Lady Stetson logo on the bottom of the right lens. This is not a sticker - the words are directly printed on the lens. These glasses are ready to be taken to an optometrist for custom lenses or to be used without lenses.
Getting prescription lenses for eyeglass frames:
All of my eyeglass frames can be given prescription lenses. They're strong and in perfect working condition, and my customers report that they work great with custom lenses. I've had buyers use them for prescription everyday frames, reading glasses, and custom sunglasses.
However, PLEASE NOTE that not every eyecare provider will supply custom lenses for vintage frames. Some large frame suppliers, like LensCrafters and Walmart, will only put lenses in the frames that they sell. 
I STRONGLY recommend giving your eyecare provider a call before purchasing, because not every optometrist will work with vintage frames for a number of reasons.

Product name: TEACHER SALE Superhero Teacher Rubber Stamp, Female Teacher Stamp, Personalized Teacher Gift - Choose Hairstyle and Accessories
Description:
Pink Pueblo's female Superhero Teacher rubber stamp is a fresh and fun teacher appreciation or end of the year gift! You get to choose the name, hairstyle and accessories for your teacher to make the stamp as personalized as possible. The stamp art is original art by Devon (that's me!) at the studio of Pink Pueblo. All stamps are hand made and hand packaged in my studio prior to shipment.
• Size: approximately 1.875x1.875"
• one wood mounted photopolymer stamp
• designed and hand made in the United States
ABOUT OUR STAMPS
Pink Pueblo custom stamps are high quality wood mounted photopolymer stamps. Our hand made stamps are permanently mounted on maple wood mounts. Please note each stamp is a custom creation and may vary slightly in size or text layout (due to length or size of text).
ABOUT OUR INK
We are proud to offer ColorBox® Premium Dye Ink by ClearSnap®. Inkpads are not automatically included with your stamp purchase; if you want to include an inkpad please select your color above. ColorBox® Premium Dye Ink is fast-drying ink that is washable with water, and dries well on glossy or coated papers. Inkpad dimensions: L 4" x W 2.5" x D .5".
HOW TO ORDER
• Please enter the text to be included on the stamp in the Message to Seller section exactly as you want the text to appear on the completed stamp. 
• Please also enter the Hairstyle of choice and Accessories of choice (see preview images) in the Message to Seller section (for example: 'straight, short with bangs and round glasses').
You'll receive a convoed digital proof of your stamp within 24 hours of purchase. Inkpads are not automatically included with your stamp purchase; if you want to include a inkpad please select your color and ink type above.
TURNAROUND TIME
Unless previously discussed, your stamp will ship 1-3 business days after proof approval via the United States Post Office. You will receive a shipping notification as soon as your package is on it's way! If you need faster shipping, please contact me. Please note stamps orders will not be cancelled or refunded after proof approval. We always offer Free Economy Shipping for our United States customers!
CARING FOR YOUR STAMP
Stored and cared for properly, your stamp will last for years. Photopolymer is prone to staining, so gently wipe your stamp with a damp cloth after use. Don't ever submerge your stamp in water, and ensure your stamp is thoroughly dry after cleaning. Store your stamp indoors and away from direct sunlight to prevent yellowing. If your stamp does stain, don't panic - this won't affect it's performance! Don't use solvent or oil-based inks, and never use harsh cleaning chemicals on your stamp.
COMMERCIAL USE
Pink Pueblo stamps may be used to decorate products or packaging for your business. However, our artwork may not be used as your logo or duplicated.
ALSO ON ETSY
Please visit our digital shop at 
pinkpueblo.etsy.com
 for personal and commercial use clipart, graphics and photography tools!

Description:
A Quick note about your designer:
Hi :)
1. I'm a perfectionist
2. Handmade should look as nice if not nicer then store bought.
3. I cherish the relationship between the crafter and customer which is something you don't get when buying from department stores.

SKIRT DETAILS
This semi-flared, a line, pull on skirt is very unique and fun! You can wear it on your hips or waist with the flexibility of the elastic waist band. I custom make each one to your exact size out of any fabric you heart desires. It features a drop waistband that is cut on the bias so there's little to no bunching from the elastic so it fits flat on your hips. All seams are finish stitched with the extra clean look of french seams along the sides. I've included detailed pictures of how my skirts look inside and out so you can really see what you'll be getting. These skirts are not quickly made for profit each one is handcrafted with care which takes time. Much attention is paid to every little detail of this skirt, all stitches are very straight and professional looking you'll notice this upon closer inspection. It's built to last years and with the bias cut elastic drop waistband it'll still fit as you may loose, or gain weight.
All Fabric is washed in my own homemade natural laundry detergent, and then dried so the fabric is preshrunk ready to be washed and dried many times. I do recommend washing in cold water and line drying to prevent fading and extending your skirts life even longer. All skirts are sewn in a smoke free pet free studio in beautiful Port Orchard Washington with a professional sewing machine.
I purchase the material for each skirt on a as needed basis and then make the size you want. Just send me your hip measurement, and desired length. Standard length is 22.5" and can be adjusted upon request. For length requests over 24"s will have a additional charge of 5 please purchase:
